article_title: New Fayette Mall store offers health care insurance through Kynect
article_text: Enter the Fayette Mall near P.F. Chang's, and you walk by the expected offerings of kids clothing stores, boot stores and cellphone kiosks. But then you'll see the Kynect store, where you can sign up for health insurance.
